hopobject.body: How many weeks' holiday a year are there? tamsulosin teva 0.4 mg "I'd argue that expanding the market [with a lower-priced iPad Mini] is even more important than having a higher-resolution tablet at that size," Gottheil said. "The slow-down in Apple's tablet sales stems from the start of a market saturation for premium-priced products, so a lower-priced [iPad Mini] is critical to maintaining growth. The question is how far they can bring down the price."
